But what about you, Father?

9
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,800
You refused to give him any grain.

10
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,040
Is it really because

11
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:47,360
the disaster in Linfen isn't severe?

12
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,510
Is it really because

13
00:01:48,510 --> 00:01:50,120
the relief grain hasn't arrived yet?

14
