Wan,

17
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,000
Han Muzhi

18
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:12,030
is uncontrollable.

19
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:13,800
Look at what he wrote.

20
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,190
Every word shows his discontent

21
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:19,160
and his shame
in being associated with us.

22
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:20,520
How can someone like that

23
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,960
join our Liu family?

24
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,600
If you marry him,

25
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,390
can he treat you well?

26
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,830
He just doesn't want to get involved

27
00:02:26,830 --> 00:02:28,550
in the tricks of the official world.

28
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:31,630
I admire and appreciate him,

29
00:02:31,670 --> 00:02:32,390
for his

30
00:02:32,390 --> 00:02:33,520
integrity

31
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,240
and purity.

32
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:36,880
If I have to marry someone

33
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:37,880
who's just a yes-man,

34
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,360
climbing up

35
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,880
by flattering others,

36
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,830
I'd rather stay single forever.

37
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:46,630
How outrageous!

38
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,030
If you want to ruin

39
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,390
my marriage to Han Muzhi,

40
00:02:57,190 --> 00:02:58,550
I'll shave my head and become a nun,

41
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:01,030
living a peaceful life

42
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:03,320
devoted to the Buddha.

43
00:03:34,550 --> 00:03:35,360
Young Master.

44
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:36,630
Should I go in first

45
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,960
to gather some intelligence?

46
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,630
No.

47
00:03:38,830 --> 00:03:39,800
Trying to probe now

48
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,160
is like walking into a trap.

49
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,320
[Qi Mansion]

50
00:03:46,110 --> 00:03:46,910
Let's go.

51
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:51,830
Hurry up.

52
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,000
This way.

53
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,640
Go with Luo Shu.

54
00:04:22,110 --> 00:04:23,600
I'm not here to run away.

55
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,790
- Young Master.
- Be careful.

56
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,070
You can really throw a punch!

57
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:33,070
Qi Menglin.

58
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:33,830
Sun Qian.

59
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:35,200
What are you doing here?

60
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,640
Take them away.

61
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,270
Yes.

62
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,790
Do you know what happened to my family?

63
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,270
Your father and family members

64
00:04:40,270 --> 00:04:41,550
have already been taken to the capital.

65
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:42,670
It's so fast.

66
00:04:43,110 --> 00:04:43,950
Mr. Sun,

67
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,320
we're back this time

68
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:46,880
to get to the bottom of this

69
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,600
and find evidence
to clear the Qi family's name.

70
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:50,790
Taiyuan now

71
00:04:50,790 --> 00:04:52,390
is under Mr. Liu's control.

72
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,760
Trying to clear the Qi family's name

73
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,830
is harder than climbing to heaven.

74
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,200
You need to plan this carefully.

75
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,440
I'm from the Qi family.

76
00:04:59,110 --> 00:05:00,350
Even if it costs me my life,

77
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:01,670
I won't back down.

78
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,230
If you need my help,

79
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,270
just let me know.

80
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:08,920
They've already slipped into Taiyuan.

81
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,640
And you didn't notice anything

82
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:10,720
from the gate tower?

83
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,480
I admit I'm incompetent.

84
00:05:12,550 --> 00:05:13,880
You're really incompetent.

85
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:16,070
There are so many eyes
at the entrance of the Qi mansion,

86
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:16,550
but you

87
00:05:16,550 --> 00:05:18,270
let Qi Menglin slip away.

88
00:05:23,670 --> 00:05:25,230
Considering our years together,

89
00:05:27,110 --> 00:05:28,160
I'll let this go this time.

90
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,350
I'll give you another chance.

91
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:32,670
If you mess up again,

92
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,270
you know the consequences.

93
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:36,950
I understand.

94
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,510
Get out.

95
00:05:54,350 --> 00:05:55,390
Be careful, Young Master.

96
00:05:58,270 --> 00:05:59,070
This way.

97
00:06:04,320 --> 00:06:05,270
This way, Young Master.

98
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,720
Watch out.

99
00:06:18,230 --> 00:06:19,200
Right there.

100
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:33,950
Young Master, Miss Luo, please.

101
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:43,110
Over here.

102
00:06:50,550 --> 00:06:52,760
This is your home?

103
00:06:55,230 --> 00:06:56,320
Didn't you live at my home

104
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,550
when you were a kid?

105
00:07:02,670 --> 00:07:03,390
When I was a kid,

106
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,880
my family was so poor
that we could hardly eat.

107
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,040
My parents sold me

108
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,230
to your family.

109
00:07:08,350 --> 00:07:10,110
They thought
at least I'd get enough to eat.

110
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:11,830
A few years later,

111
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,230
my parents passed away.

112
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,390
I

113
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,440
never cared about

114
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,510
your family.

115
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,040
It's okay.

116
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,270
That's all in the past.

117
00:07:29,230 --> 00:07:30,040
Young Master,

118
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:32,070
this house has been empty for years.

119
00:07:32,070 --> 00:07:33,600
No one knows here.

120
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,880
It's tough for you to stay here.

121
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,390
I'm sorry.

122
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,510
Even in this mess,

123
00:07:41,950 --> 00:07:43,550
you're still with me,

124
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:44,920
through thick and thin.

125
00:07:49,230 --> 00:07:52,480
And you took a beating
to protect me.

126
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,480
In the next life,

127
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:03,920
you be the master,

128
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:05,830
and I'll be your servant.

129
00:08:09,670 --> 00:08:11,600
Young Master, please spare me.

130
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:14,160
Your sweet talk is too much.

131
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:16,160
I have goosebumps all over.

132
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:19,390
Having a place to stay

133
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:20,600
is already great.

134
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,040
I'll go

135
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,550
buy some supplies tomorrow.

136
00:08:28,270 --> 00:08:29,270
No candles.

137
00:08:29,350 --> 00:08:30,670
This place hasn't been lived in
for a while.

138
00:08:30,670 --> 00:08:31,510
If lights suddenly appear,

139
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:32,760
it'll attract attention.

140
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,110
The best way to stay hidden

141
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:35,440
is to keep things the same

142
00:08:35,590 --> 00:08:36,910
and limit comings and goings.

143
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,230
What are you thinking about?

144
00:08:59,590 --> 00:09:00,440
I'm thinking

145
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,760
about how they got started.

146
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:10,880
Young Master,

147
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,790
you really need to think this through.

148
00:09:13,110 --> 00:09:14,670
Misusing military grain
is a serious crime.

149
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:15,590
If you get caught,

150
00:09:15,590 --> 00:09:16,960
you could lose your head.

151
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,910
Don't worry.

152
00:09:19,590 --> 00:09:20,960
My father manages the military grain.

153
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,960
Even if I get caught,

154
00:09:23,590 --> 00:09:25,150
he'll cover for me.

155
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,550
But what if he doesn't want

156
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:28,080
to help you?

157
00:09:29,590 --> 00:09:30,400
I mean,

158
00:09:30,760 --> 00:09:31,470
what if he can't

159
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:32,880
help you out?

160
00:09:34,590 --> 00:09:36,080
The document is forged by me.

161
00:09:37,150 --> 00:09:38,440
The grain is taken by me.

162
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,840
Even if he can't cover for me,

163
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:45,520
at worst, I'll lose my head.

164
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:47,400
It's worth

165
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:49,320
risking my life

166
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,030
to save so many others.

167
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,200
Young Master,

168
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,150
stop pretending

169
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:53,320
to be so righteous.

170
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,030
Aren't you doing this for Miss Luo?

171
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,150
Those aren't mutually exclusive.

172
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,200
It makes me

173
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,670
want to do this even more.

174
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:05,640
Young Master, what do you want?

175
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:09,960
Peace of mind.

176
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:11,880
Though I haven't been a commandant

177
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:12,790
for long,

178
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,670
I've seen

179
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,000
the suffering of the people.

180
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,470
Now that the villagers are in trouble,

181
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,520
how can I just stand by?

182
00:10:22,230 --> 00:10:23,030
What's more,

183
00:10:24,030 --> 00:10:25,200
I've already vowed with Luo Shu

184
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,230
to be together for life.

185
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,200
I can't let her

186
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,590
fight this battle alone.

187
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,550
Young Master, you're so foolish.

188
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,000
Fools have their blessings.

189
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,080
Go quickly.

190
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:40,000
Get the carts and boats ready

191
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:40,670
for transporting grain.

192
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:41,710
Okay.

193
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:37,000
[Governor's Warrant]

194
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,470
- Mr. Menglin.
- Mr. Menglin.

195
00:11:56,670 --> 00:11:57,670
What brings you here?

196
00:11:58,790 --> 00:12:00,030
Tonight, we're

197
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:01,280
on duty at Mr. Qi's courtyard.

198
00:12:02,710 --> 00:12:04,550
On duty? That's great!

199
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,440
You all carry on. I'm leaving.

200
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,000
Mr. Menglin,

201
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,110
how come

202
00:12:09,110 --> 00:12:10,640
you're in Mr. Qi's courtyard?

203
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:14,880
How dare you!

204
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:16,670
Who do you think you are to question me?

205
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:18,840
Forgive me, Mr. Menglin.

206
00:12:19,110 --> 00:12:22,000
I'm just doing my duty.

207
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,640
Can't I just see my father?

208
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,150
But Mr. Qi said,

209
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:27,790
without his order,

210
00:12:27,790 --> 00:12:29,760
no one can enter the study.

211
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,640
What do you mean?

212
00:12:31,110 --> 00:12:31,760
Are you suspecting

213
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:33,110
that I'm stealing from the study?

214
00:12:33,550 --> 00:12:34,470
No!

215
00:12:34,470 --> 00:12:36,470
Mr. Menglin, I didn't mean that at all.

216
00:12:36,470 --> 00:12:37,200
Since that's the case,

217
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,350
just get out of the way!

218
00:12:38,590 --> 00:12:40,400
I wouldn't dare! This won't do.

219
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:41,790
Do you have any respect for your place?

220
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,320
Are you trying to bully Mr. Menglin?

221
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,350
I wouldn't dare!

222
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,200
Mr. Menglin!

223
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:53,200
Well said!

224
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:54,840
Make sure to discipline

225
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,080
these two who lack manners.

226
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:58,110
Mr. Menglin,

227
00:12:58,960 --> 00:13:00,030
please don't make it hard for us.

228
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:01,280
You two are just waiting

229
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:02,470
for Mr. Qi to return and judge you,

230
00:13:02,470 --> 00:13:03,590
right?

231
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,590
I...

232
00:13:08,230 --> 00:13:09,110
I wouldn't dare!

233
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:11,030
Mr. Menglin, I offended you.

234
00:13:11,030 --> 00:13:12,670
I was wrong!

235
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:14,000
We both realize our mistakes.

236
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:14,880
So hurry and leave!

237
00:13:15,710 --> 00:13:16,910
Okay! We're going!

238
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,320
Mr. Menglin, do you have something?

239
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:25,910
What could I have?

240
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:27,790
By the way,

241
00:13:28,710 --> 00:13:29,520
where's Yanjin?

242
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:31,400
Why didn't I see him with you?

243
00:13:31,470 --> 00:13:33,710
Mr. Yanjin has important business today.

244
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:35,230
Important business?

245
00:13:35,590 --> 00:13:36,440
What's that about?

246
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:38,400
I'm not sure.

247
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,880
Why not wait for Mr. Yanjin to come back

248
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:41,150
and ask him yourself?

249
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:42,910
No need for that.

250
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,440
If my father and Yanjin

251
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,280
ask about me,

252
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,880
just say you haven't seen me today.

253
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:54,080
Yes, Mr. Menglin.

254
00:13:58,910 --> 00:14:00,230
By order of Governor Qi,

255
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,670
I'm here to requisition some grain.

256
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:10,880
Who are you?

257
00:14:11,230 --> 00:14:13,350
I'm Governor Qi's third son, Qi Menglin.

258
00:14:13,590 --> 00:14:14,280
Please, Mr. Menglin.

259
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:14,910
Wait.

260
00:14:16,640 --> 00:14:18,230
What's going on here?

261
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:20,640
This is an official business.

262
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,350
Why would Governor Qi

263
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:24,000
send Mr. Menglin to requisition grain?

264
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,280
Besides, this document

265
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:27,200
[Governor's Warrant]
is not in the governor's handwriting.

266
00:14:28,230 --> 00:14:29,840
Do you recognize
the Governor Qi's handwriting?

267
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,880
I used to be a personal retainer
of Governor Qi.

268
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,000
Then how can you

269
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,320
not recognize Mr. Menglin?

270
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,470
It's been years since we last met;

271
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:37,440
I might not recognize him.

272
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:39,550
You're overthinking it.

273
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,550
This document
has Governor Qi's official seal.

274
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:42,790
What's more,

275
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:44,670
the son of Governor Qi

276
00:14:44,790 --> 00:14:46,400
is not someone we can offend.

277
00:14:46,710 --> 00:14:48,470
But if something goes wrong,

278
00:14:48,470 --> 00:14:49,960
we won't be able to handle it.

279
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:50,960
What are you mumbling about?

280
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:52,440
Do you want me to have my father

281
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,320
come in person?

282
00:14:54,790 --> 00:14:56,150
I wouldn't dare.

283
00:14:56,150 --> 00:14:57,030
Hurry and get the grain.

284
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,550
Please, Mr. Menglin.

285
00:15:03,110 --> 00:15:04,110
Commandant Qi, please.

286
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,840
Be careful, don't spill any.

287
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:15,760
Quick!

288
00:15:20,030 --> 00:15:21,030
Take a couple fewer steps. Come on!

289
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,000
Put some more effort in, hurry!

290
